## Careful mode

When the user prefixes a prompt with `[CAREFUL MODE]` (or sets
`ROLEPOD_CAREFUL=1` and runs through `rolepod-gemini.sh`):

- Run all 5 simplicity questions explicitly before every commit
- Run all 5 test questions explicitly
- External reviewer required for auth/billing/migration changes
- Smaller increments: ≤3 files per commit, not ≤5
- Mandatory peer review even for small diffs
